Times Mirror, La Opinion Complete Deal: Times Mirror Co. has completed its 
purchase of 50% of Lozano Enterprises, which owns Los Angeles-based La Opinion, 
the nation's largest Spanish-language daily newspaper. 
</P>
<P>
