Coliseum at Sunday's Raider-Bear game, where 31 fans were arrested and 88 
ejected. JOE KENNEDY / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Police presence was evident at 
Sunday's Raider game, where security was increased one week after a fan was 
beaten severely. JOSE GALVEZ / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
