GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; PROPOSITION 131 (INCUMBENCY LIMITATION); PROPOSITION 140 
(INCUMBENCY LIMITATION); VAN DE KAMP, JOHN K; SCHABARUM, PETE; INCUMBENTS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
