UNITED STATES; FIRST AMENDMENT; DISCRIMINATION; AMERICANS ABROAD; UNITED STATES 
-- LAWS; REPORTERS; LIBEL 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA100290-0134 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 286464 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 2, 1990, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 20; Column 1; National Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
