<HEADLINE>
<P>
SOVIET ARMED FORCES CHIEF WELCOMED IN U.S. 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By United Press International 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
WASHINGTON 
</P>
