</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA100290-0137 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 286473 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 2, 1990, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 25; Column 2; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
