</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Residents are invited to attend a forum for mayoral and City Council candidates 
tonight at the Garden Grove Community Center, 11300 Stanford Ave. 
</P>
<P>
The two mayoral and seven council candidates will answer questions that have 
been submitted by residents and the candidates themselves. A reception will 
follow the question-and-answer session, which will be moderated by Chamber of 
