<P>
Other top performers: 
</P>
<P>
* Denisha Bendz, a Costa Mesa cross-country runner who ran 18 minutes 14 
seconds for three miles to win the Division III race at the Dana Hills 
Invitational Saturday. 
</P>
<P>
* Misty Hartung and Heather Lowe, who were each all-tournament selections after 
helping Cypress to the championship of the Orange Tournament. Cypress defeated 
Loara, 11-2, 4-11, 11-1, in the final Saturday. 
</P>
<P>
