seconds for three miles to win the Division II race at the Dana Hills 
Invitational Saturday. 
</P>
<P>
* Shelley Taylor, an Edison cross-country runner who ran her best time -- 17:02 
for three miles -- to win the Division I race at the Dana Hills Invitational 
Saturday. 
