<DATE>
<P>
October 2, 1990, Tuesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<P>
JAN MITTERMEIER 
</P>
<SECTION>
<P>
View; Part E; Page 1; Column 2; View Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
1437 words 
</P>
